  "content": "<p data-pid=\"jQNCsreK\">看了一下高赞答案，我觉得如何做好错题本的大方向已经定下，我就说说如何利用好错题吧！</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p data-pid=\"JYdcYD-p\">首先，做完的错题本一定要复习！这个过程决定了你错题本80%效果。没有复习，错题本就只是一个写满错题的金山，但是这金山是被埋没的金山。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p data-pid=\"3j1vQx0D\">其次，一定要有规律的复习！复习间隔太长，会使你看错题跟看新题一样，除了知道答案，中间的思考过程全被遗忘了。复习间隔太短，又会觉得乏味而浪费时间。</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p data-pid=\"vLgEueHp\">或许你会问，怎样才算有规律的复习呢？我这里就介绍一下一个知识记忆软件——Anki。不要小瞧这个软件，TA不仅能用于记忆单词、专业知识、平时的想法，还能用于规划复习！</p><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><p data-pid=\"0vfa1gbo\">先上个图</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b24ad61952d4548ce181cccd31b22616_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"794\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee4bef058515551e96beee01d3d0a095\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-77983ca368c43afe88fdc948d81ce4a4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"794\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b24ad61952d4548ce181cccd31b22616_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;794&#39; height=&#39;793&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"794\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-ee4bef058515551e96beee01d3d0a095\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-77983ca368c43afe88fdc948d81ce4a4_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"794\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b24ad61952d4548ce181cccd31b22616_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b24ad61952d4548ce181cccd31b22616_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b74ed526cb1a21133738af1553f9c87_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"794\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-99e3c06bdaeaf7eb1cc3ae3d498c02e0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-858552deb33686bb2e075df1e7d6a1e9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"794\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0b74ed526cb1a21133738af1553f9c87_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;794&#39; height=&#39;793&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"794\" data-rawheight=\"793\" data-original-token=\"v2-99e3c06bdaeaf7eb1cc3ae3d498c02e0\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-858552deb33686bb2e075df1e7d6a1e9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"794\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-0b74ed526cb1a21133738af1553f9c87_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-0b74ed526cb1a21133738af1553f9c87_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"uChblx2j\">这个是电脑版</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b52c0baf974f5629cafec44445b6f42b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1394\" data-rawheight=\"2454\" data-original-token=\"v2-7fc8abf2d2e14373595610ee5103d069\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e27c3fe5b7474983bf0eef6f3cec0d0f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1394\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b52c0baf974f5629cafec44445b6f42b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1394&#39; height=&#39;2454&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1394\" data-rawheight=\"2454\" data-original-token=\"v2-7fc8abf2d2e14373595610ee5103d069\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-e27c3fe5b7474983bf0eef6f3cec0d0f_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1394\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-b52c0baf974f5629cafec44445b6f42b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-b52c0baf974f5629cafec44445b6f42b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"TB5lpKUU\">这个是安卓版。</p><p data-pid=\"tbspkL2o\">将你的错题提炼出错误点，再设计成问题制作成Anki卡片，anki就会自动帮你安排好复习时间，并且根据每一次你对错题的熟练程度，改变记忆曲线！</p><p data-pid=\"fSg_7QMu\">再发发我的卡片</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cce64fe5cba9dbb8699cedf29647930_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1006\" data-rawheight=\"796\" data-original-token=\"v2-58e9db80c12a180aea79c39c5f04d0c3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a770627dc3313d4ed75d7703ee632400_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1006\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4cce64fe5cba9dbb8699cedf29647930_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1006&#39; height=&#39;796&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1006\" data-rawheight=\"796\" data-original-token=\"v2-58e9db80c12a180aea79c39c5f04d0c3\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-a770627dc3313d4ed75d7703ee632400_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1006\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-4cce64fe5cba9dbb8699cedf29647930_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4cce64fe5cba9dbb8699cedf29647930_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><hr/><p data-pid=\"s4N86FC2\">说了这么多（我的文章都没这么多字），推荐一下我的专栏</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/ankigaokao\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-31006511123dc6bc074c75ee9cb71bc2_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1180\" data-image-height=\"1180\" class=\"internal\">高考╳Anki——科学备考研究所</a><p data-pid=\"qG9221D2\">内有更多关于Anki与高考相结合的文章与资源，欢迎高中生关注和分享！</p>",
